summary: Once every few years I drop a post about how much I liked the dynamic between Peter and Nick Fury in the Ultimate Spider-man...
body:
Once every few years I drop a post about how much I liked the dynamic between Peter and Nick Fury in the Ultimate Spider-man Comics (even if the rest of the ultimate line I felt was too “edgy” to take) and how I REALLY wanted to see some of that in the MCU or at the very least fanfic. But I never really excpected anything to come of it? The movies seemed to want to focus more on Peter and Tony’s dynamic and the fandom didn’t seem that interested?

And then that trailer dropped.

I. Am. Very excite. Please movie, please do me a solid and give me the exploration of the Peter and Nick dynamic I have wanted for so long.
